gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：唔食得辣"},{"pid":"26ad1710b214fe6446c03be5f3873ff68e95b25d","tid":808491,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:14:27.000Z","msg":"小辣係正"}]}